extendedInfo.description: ************ This app is no longer supported************This application is intended for the education of all on the healing art known as Reiki. Reiki is a hands on healing modality that has been around since the dawn of man. This app connects you with YouTube videos on Reiki, Psychic info, and with a person who wishes to send you healing energy via her facebook, email, or her call receptionist. Reiki aids healing on all levels including spiritual, mental, emotional, and physical ( yes physical). If you have never heard about this beautiful hands on healing energy, check out this app and get connected.
